## =========================================== // LITE XL //

## Navigation

- **Move Cursor**: Arrow keys
- **Scroll Page**: Page Up, Page Down
- **Go to Line**: `Ctrl + G`

## Editing

- **Copy**: `Ctrl + C`
- **Cut**: `Ctrl + X`
- **Paste**: `Ctrl + V`
- **Undo**: `Ctrl + Z`
- **Redo**: `Ctrl + Y`

## Search and Replace

- **Find**: `Ctrl + F`
- **Find Next**: `F3`
- **Replace**: `Ctrl + H`

## Saving and Quitting

- **Save**: `Ctrl + S`
- **Save As**: `Ctrl + Shift + S`
- **Quit**: `Ctrl + Q`

## Appearance Settings

### Change Colorscheme

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set colorscheme <colorscheme_name>` and press Enter.

### Adjust Font Size

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set font_size <size>` and press Enter.

### Toggle Line Numbers

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set show_line_numbers true` or `set show_line_numbers false` to toggle.

### Change Theme

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set theme <theme_name>` and press Enter.

### Adjust Tab Size

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set tab_size <size>` and press Enter.

### Change Syntax Highlighting

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set syntax <language>` to specify syntax highlighting.

### Customize Keybindings

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set key <key_combination> <command>` to customize keybindings.

### Set Auto Indentation

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set auto_indent true` or `set auto_indent false` to toggle.

### Adjust Line Wrapping

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set line_wrap true` or `set line_wrap false` to toggle.

### Change Cursor Style

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set cursor_style <style>` to choose a cursor style (e.g., block, line, underline).

### Toggle Sidebar

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set show_sidebar true` or `set show_sidebar false` to toggle sidebar visibility.

### Change Line Height

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set line_height <height>` to adjust line height.

### Modify Status Bar

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set show_status_bar true` or `set show_status_bar false` to toggle.

### Customize Indentation Style

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set indent_style <style>` to choose spaces or tabs.

### Enable Spell Checking

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set spell_check true` or `set spell_check false` to toggle spell checking.

### Adjust Scrollbar Visibility

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set show_scrollbar true` or `set show_scrollbar false` to toggle.

### Set Word Wrap

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set word_wrap true` or `set word_wrap false` to toggle word wrapping.

### Change Highlighting for Current Line

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set highlight_current_line true` or `set highlight_current_line false` to toggle.

### Adjust Bracket Matching

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set bracket_matching true` or `set bracket_matching false` to toggle bracket matching.

### Customize Toolbar

- Open Lite XL and press `Alt + Enter` to open the command prompt.
- Type `set show_toolbar true` or `set show_toolbar false` to toggle toolbar visibility.

## ==================================== / CMD TABLES //

| **Command**                    | **Description**                                  |
|--------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| `set colorscheme <name>`       | Change colorscheme                               |
| `set font_size <size>`         | Adjust font size                                 |
| `set show_line_numbers true/false` | Toggle line numbers                        |
| `set theme <name>`             | Change editor theme                              |
| `set tab_size <size>`          | Set tab size                                     |
| `set auto_indent true/false`   | Enable or disable auto indentation               |
| `set line_wrap true/false`     | Enable or disable line wrapping                  |
| `set spell_check true/false`   | Enable or disable spell checking                 |
| `set word_wrap true/false`     | Toggle word wrap                                 |
| `set bracket_matching true/false` | Toggle bracket matching                    |
| `set show_toolbar true/false`  | Show or hide toolbar                             |

